<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EchoStream – Child Safety Standards</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        }
        .hero-bg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e2937 0%, #0f172a 100%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-950 text-gray-200">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="hero-bg border-b border-gray-800">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-waveform text-white text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">EchoStream</h1>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Safe • Anonymous • Real</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm">
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Home</a>
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Privacy Policy</a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-blue-400 font-medium">Child Safety</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <div class="mb-10">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Child Safety Standards</h1>
            <p class="text-blue-400 text-lg">EchoStream – Child Safety Policy</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
                EchoStream is committed to protecting children and maintaining a safe platform. 
                We enforce a <strong class="text-red-400">strict zero-tolerance policy</strong> toward any content that involves child sexual abuse or exploitation (CSAE).
            </p>

            <!-- Zero Tolerance -->
            <div class="mt-12 bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-red-500">1.</span> Zero-Tolerance Policy
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4 text-gray-300">
                    EchoStream strictly prohibits any content that depicts, promotes, facilitates, or references child sexual abuse or exploitation. This includes:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
                        Sexual content involving minors
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
                        Grooming, solicitation, or exploitation of minors
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
                        Requests for sexual images or interactions involving minors
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
                        Any attempt to direct users to CSAE material
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Reporting In-App -->
            <div class="mt-10 bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-400">2.</span> Reporting In-App
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300">
                    Users can report content directly within the EchoStream app using the Report feature on posts and profiles. 
                    Reports are reviewed promptly and may result in content removal, account suspension, or permanent bans.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- External Reporting -->
            <div class="mt-10 bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-400">3.</span> External Reporting
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4 text-gray-300">
                    If you believe a child is in immediate danger, contact local emergency services. 
                    Suspected CSAE can also be reported to the National Center for Missing &amp; Exploited Children (NCMEC) CyberTipline:
                </p>
                <a href="https://www.missingkids.org/gethelpnow/cybertipline" 
                   target="_blank"
                   class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 transition text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium">
                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                    Report to NCMEC CyberTipline
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Enforcement -->
            <div class="mt-10 bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-400">4.</span> Enforcement
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300">
                    EchoStream actively monitors and investigates reports of CSAE. Violations result in immediate removal of content and permanent account termination. 
                    Relevant cases may be reported to appropriate authorities.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Contact -->
            <div class="mt-10 bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-400">5.</span> Contact
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                    For questions regarding child safety or compliance, contact:
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                    <a href="mailto:echosteram@gmail.com" 
                       class="flex-1 bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 transition rounded-2xl p-5 group">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-envelope text-blue-400"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Email</p>
                                <p class="font-medium text-white group-hover:text-blue-400">echosteram@gmail.com</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center text-xs text-gray-500">
            Last updated: June 2026<br>
            EchoStream by Nachman Zeida Rosenberg • United States
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-black py-8 border-t border-gray-900">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center text-xs text-gray-500">
            ©️ 2026 EchoStream. All rights reserved.<br>
            This policy is part of our commitment to a safe community.
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Tailwind script already loaded via CDN
    </script>
</body>
</html>
